By Andile Mngxitama Taiwan, South Korea, Japan and China – their technological advances are based on radical land and agrarian transformation. Here in SA landless people talk confidently about the 4IR. University professors want to jump the stage of land return and parachute into the 4IR. It’s a cruel myth driven by cowardice. At best their 4IR will serve land thieves…. Andile Mngxitama is the President of Black First Land First (BLF), a radical black consciousness organization.